  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Login with WiFi, enter any channel\r\n2. Make sure the last message written in the channel is yours\r\n3. Disconnect from WiFi and wait for the disconnected banner to popup\r\n4. Write a group of messages, The Resend label should appear\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe Resend label should appear for each message that wasn't delivered\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n if you have written a message before, the resend button will not appear, since the message gets grouped with the previous message header (containing username and time).\r\n<img width=\"399\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/197944868-cd6b3363-e2ee-4ba6-bcb6-ba3a7c36374b.png\">\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/7749\r\n- Operating System: macOS Monterey\r\n\r\n",
